dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 10 meter contour interval and spot hights. Map shows district boundaries, railways, 3 classes of roads, telegraph lines, temples, pagodas, vegetation, and land features, In upper margin 1:25,000. Grid no. 2. In lower left margin: [Series] HIND: 1014. Reg. 2561 D'42-5,000.
